keyValuePair.Value: Boss, I feel I have been progressing and I would like to discuss my wages. I feel I should be earning more based on my contribution to the team. I would really appreciate it if you would arrange a meeting with me and my agent so we can go over my contract.

Boss, I feel I have been progressing and I would like to discuss my wages. I feel I should be earning more based on my contribution to the team. I would really appreciate it if you would arrange a meeting with me and my agent so we can go over my contract.
You're a key player in my squad and I'll arrange something soon.
We'll get to it soon enough
I have other things on my plate now, but we should get talking about new terms for your contract soon enough.
You should focus on your football
I think you need to spend more time thinking about football and less about money. Focus on your game and you get the recogniton you deserve in due course.
Glad to see that my value in the squad is recognized, boss. It'll help ease my mind and focus only on my football moving forward.
Glad to see that my value in the squad is recognized, boss. It'll help ease my mind and focus only on my football moving forward.
Glad to hear you're finally at peace. Now get out there and prove you're worth the money
Now that your wage concerns are finally out of the way let's get back to work.
You should only worry about football
Football should be your only concern. Day in, day out. Always stay hungry for winning games and money will surely follow.
